headline.print_headline: Coroner: Priest Beaten to Death With Stake, Pipe
headline.main: Coroner: Priest Beaten to Death With Stake, Pipe

lead_paragraph: A beloved priest who was killed in the Northern California city of Eureka was beaten to death with a wooden stake and a metal gutter pipe, his autopsy shows.
